address2: 30th Floor, Room B&C 1 Wang Kwong Road Kowloon Bay
longBusinessSummary: Inspur Digital Enterprise Technology Limited, an investment holding company, provides software development and other software services, and cloud services in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Cloud Services, Management Software, and Internet of things (IoT) Solution segments. It is also involved in the sale of information technology peripherals and software; and property investment activities. The company was formerly known as Inspur International Limited and changed its name to Inspur Digital Enterprise Technology Limited in January 2023. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong. Inspur Digital Enterprise Technology Limited is a subsidiary of Inspur Group Limited.
